reviewText: Two of the films are very good and interesting. Besame Mucho is more like a soap opera with no depth.

No es lo que yo esperaba, es un drama de una prostituta que vive en Barcelona pero no le veo algo bueno. Yo crea que iba a ser parecida a la pelcula "Whisky"  "El Ultimo Tren" que son pelculas uruguayas muy buenas.
DVD quality was vary good & condition also the same but movie it self was O.K after watching movie sold it to a movier trader but seller was great and prompted will buy in future more from seller.
